<F P=100> SYRIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yemeni Presidential Council Delegation Visits </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yemeni Presidential Council Delegation Visits </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Meets With Khaddam </H4>

<F P=102> JN0804195994 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1815 GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0804195994 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Vice President 'Abd-al-Halim Khaddam received Salim 
Salih Muhammad, member of the Yemeni Presidential Council and 
assistant secretary general of the Yemeni Socialist Party [YSP], 
and Dr. 'Abd-al-'Aziz al-Dali, member of the YSP Political 
Bureau and secretary of foreign relations, at 1800 today. 
Foreign Minister Faruq al-Shar' and Yemeni Ambassador in 
Damascus Muhammad 'Abduh Shutfah attended the meeting. 
  Talks dealt with the situation in Yemen. The vice president 
indicated Syria's eagerness to maintain Yemeni unity and 
stressed the need to resolve the Yemeni crisis through brotherly 
dialogue that averts the dangers of bloody conflicts. 

</TEXT>

