<H3> <TI>   Al-Baz Returns From U.S. Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Al-Baz Returns From U.S. Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1104182694 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1535 GMT 11 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1104182694 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 11 Apr (MENA)--Dr. Usamah al-Baz, Foreign 
Ministry first under secretary and director of the President's 
Office for Political Affairs, returned to Cairo this afternoon 
after a week-long visit to the United States. 
  During his visit al-Baz discussed the current peace efforts 
and Egyptian-U.S. ties with U.S. Secretary of State Warren 
Christopher. 
  He also discussed with senior White House officials the 
recent developments of the Middle East peace operation. 

</TEXT>

