to our correspondent this morning, he said Labor had promised 
that through the peace process, it would remove terror from 
within the boundaries of the Green Line. According to him, 
since the State of Israel was founded, the state of security has 
not been as unstable as it is now. He added that he supports 
the closure but, according to him, the government has been 
pulling Israel Army soldiers out of certain places in the 
territories and replacing them with the terrorists' army. Such 
acts are stupid and dangerous to the citizens of Israel, 
Netanyahu said. 

