<H3> <TI>   Arab Woman Fatally Shot by Israeli in West Bank </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Arab Woman Fatally Shot by Israeli in West Bank </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1204092794 Tel Aviv IDF Radio in Hebrew 0900 GMT 12 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA1204092794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tel Aviv IDF Radio </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] An Arab woman was fatally shot by an Israeli truck 
driver in the territories today. The incident occurred near the 
village of al-Jib, south of Ramallah. 
  Our correspondent in the territories Golan Yokhpaz reports 
that the man was driving a Coca-Cola truck along the Pisgat 
Ze'ev road in the direction of al-Ram junction when local 
residents apparently threw stones at the truck. The driver 
fired several shots from his handgun, killing a local woman on 
the spot. The commander of the Judaea Region police reported 
that searches to find the driver are currently under way. 

</TEXT>

