<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Truckloads' of Palestinian Ammunition Seized </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1204055194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0430 GMT 12 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1204055194 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Army forces yesterday raided an ammunition store 
belonging to a Palestinian group in the Sharhabil neighborhood 
of Sidon and confiscated around five truckloads of ammunition. 
The ammunition included: Some 343 107-mm rockets; 915 
artillery rounds of various calibers; 271 shell charges; 138 
hand grenades; and 6,680 rounds of various types of ammunition. 
  The Army forces are continuing to search for weapons and 
ammunition throughout the Lebanese areas. 

