<H3> <TI>   'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam Claims Responsibility </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam Claims Responsibility </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1304084494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0838 GMT 13 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1304084494 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] We have just learned that 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam has 
assumed responsibility for the Hadera attack. They placed a 
telephone call to Qol Yisra'el -- that is how brazen they are -- 
and speaking in Arabic, they made their announcement that 
'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam assumes responsibility for this attack. 

</TEXT>

