<F P=100> SYRIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Receives Delegation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Minister Receives Delegation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1204161694 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1515 GMT 12 Apr 94 </F>

