  [Text] Al-'Ayn, 13 Apr (WAKH) -- His Highness Shaykh Zayid 
Bin-Sultan Al Nuhayyn, president of the United Arab Emirates 
[UAE], has received a written message from Ukrainian President 
Leonid Kravchuk. The message deals with relations of 
cooperation and friendship between the two countries and ways of 
enhancing them. 
