<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Turkish Interior Minister Concludes Talks, Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Al-Asad Receives Mentese </H4>

<F P=102> JN1304145294 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1415 GMT 13 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1304145294 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At 1100 today, President Hafiz al-Asad received 
Turkish Interior Minister Nahit Mentese and his accompanying 
delegation. The meeting was attended by Interior Minister Dr. 
Muhammad Harbah and the Turkish ambassador in Damascus. 
  Mentese conveyed to President Hafiz al-Asad greetings from 
Turkish President Suleyman Demirel and Prime Minister Tansu 
Ciller. President al-Asad asked him to convey his greetings to 
