<F P=102>   JN1304154594 Amman Radio Jordan Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 
13 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1304154594 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman Radio Jordan Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] His Majesty King Husayn saw off His Excellency 
Austrian President Thomas Klestil and his delegation when they 
departed Amman this afternoon, concluding an official three-day 
visit to the Kingdom. 
  During the visit, the Austrian president held talks with His 
Majesty King Husayn and senior officials. The talks focused on 
several regional and international issues of common interest, 
developments in the Middle East peace process, and the 
distinguished relations between the two friendly countries. His 
excellency also visited several cultural landmarks in Jordan. 
  The Austrian president was also seen off by His Highness 
Crown Prince Hasan, His Highness Prince 'Abdallah Bin-al-Husayn, 
Prime Minister Dr. 'Abd-al-Salam al-Majali, and a number of 
senior officials. 

