<H3> <TI>   Syrian Spokesman Rejects Rabin's Format Proposals </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Syrian Spokesman Rejects Rabin's Format Proposals </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1304071294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0600 GMT 13 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1304071294 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Syria has rejected Prime Minister Rabin's proposals 
to change the format of the Syrian-Israeli negotiations. An 
official Syrian spokesman has said that secret talks and 
separate agreements will weaken the Arabs and allow Israel to 
force its terms on them. 
  The Syrian spokesman further said that the agreement Israel 
signed with the PLO did not lead to peace. Rather, it 
complicated the situation and increased the agony of the Arabs 
in the territories. 

</TEXT>

