<H3> <TI>   Terrorist Said Among Casualties of Hadera Attack </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Terrorist Said Among Casualties of Hadera Attack </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1304154094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1500 GMT 13 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1304154094 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Six people were killed this morning and 30 
others wounded in a bomb explosion aboard a bus in Hadera. 
Among the six killed was apparently the terrorist himself. 
Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] has claimed responsibility 
and says more attacks can be expected. Most of those hurt 
sustained light injuries, and most of those have already been 
released from hospital. In Hadera demonstrators protested 
against the violence and government policy. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

