<F P=101> Algeria </F>
<H3> <TI>   Bouira Province Governor Escapes Assassination Attempt </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bouira Province Governor Escapes Assassination Attempt </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1304123694 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1200 
GMT 13 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1304123694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Brahim Ben Gayou, governor of the Province of 
Bouira, has had a narrow escape from an assassination attempt. 
The security services said that he had a narrow escape from an 
assassination attempt committed this morning by unknown 
individuals near his home when he was preparing himself to leave 
for work accompanied by his driver. The same services added 
that the governor was slightly injured while his driver suffered 
various injuries after which he was taken to Bouira hospital to 
have preliminary treatment before the evacuation of the two of 
them to Ain Naaja military hospital in Algiers. 

</TEXT>

