<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Urayqat Holds Israel Responsible for Violence </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Urayqat Holds Israel Responsible for Violence </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1404192194 Sanaa Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1800 GMT 14 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1404192194 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Voice of Palestine </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Dr. Sa'ib 'Urayqat, head of the Palestinian 
delegation to the peace negotiations, has held Israel fully 
responsible for the escalation of acts of violence in the 
occupied territories. In a statement last night, 'Urayqat was 
quoted as saying that the acts of violence are generated by the 
Israeli occupation troops' daily massacres targeting the 
Palestinian people. He stressed that ending the Israeli 
occupation of the occupied territories and halting the Israeli 
Army's acts of terrorism is the only way to end the acts of 
violence. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

